ss=\"one-third\">\r\n<div class=\"dashicons dashicons-welcome-widgets-menus\"></div>\r\n<h4>Custom Widgets</h4>\r\n<p>The Genesis Framework is widgetized beyond just the sidebar, so we developed custom widgets to use on any area of your site.\r\n</p></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"one-third\">\r\n<div class=\"dashicons dashicons-feedback\"></div>\r\n<h4>Layout Options</h4>\r\n<p>You can \"mix and match\" your layout, meaning you can easily choose any of the three layouts for each one of your individual pages or posts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-third first\">\r\n<div class=\"dashicons dashicons-wordpress-alt\"></div><h4>WordPress and Theme Tutorials</h4>\r\n<p>Want to go a bit further with WordPress? Want to get even more out of Genesis? Our tutorials will teach you all you need to know.\r\n</p></div>\r\n<div class=\"one-third\">\r\n<div class=\"dashicons dashicons-cloud\"></div>\r\n<h4>Instant Updates</h4>\r\n<p>Updating WordPress / Genesis is a snap: one click and you\'re done. We test all updates thoroughly, so you\'re not playing guinea pig. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"one-third\">\r\n<div class=\"dashicons dashicons-translation\"></div>\r\n<h4>Translation Ready</h4>\r\n<p> Need Genesis in another language? The framework is translation-ready, making it as easy as possible for you to get work done. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:5;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:12:\"Our Partners\";s:4:\"text\";s:518:\"<div class=\"one-fourth first\">\r\n<img src=\"http://demo.studiopress.com/centric/files/2014/01/logo-genesis.png\" alt=\"Genesis\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"one-fourth\">\r\n<img src=\"http://demo.studiopress.com/centric/files/2014/01/logo-studiopress.png\" alt=\"\"/>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"one-fourth\">\r\n<img src=\"http://demo.studiopress.com/centric/files/2014/01/logo-wordpress.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"one-fourth\">\r\n<img src=\"http://demo.studiopress.com/centric/files/2014/01/logo-copyblogger.png\" alt=\"\" /